【Bendable Branch DIY】3D structure branches make lighted tree looks like Blossom which will not limit your imagination and creation, a strong festive atmosphere can be easily created.

【Energy Saving】LED lights meet the need of brightness, energy saving and long life up to 30000 hours. 24 V UL adapter safe with low voltage power.
【Multiple Occasions】Convenient installation and movement, pre-lit birch trees can be reused. Suitable for Home/Festival/Party/Christmas decoration.
description: Product Introduction:

Lighted tree is also called LED landscape lighting tree or LED artificial tree. With advantages of energy saving and long life span. LED trees is environment friendly and reusable. With its unique, elegant & magnificent modeling, LED light tree are PERFECT choice for festivals, Christmas, parties, and so on.
Package includes:
1* Birch Tree Light;1* Power adapter; 1* User manual;
If the lights do not work?
1. Make sure lights are connected to the adaptor2. Make sure connectors are fully inserted to the adaptor3. Make sure the transformer is plugged into a 120 V AC outlet
FAQ:
Q:
How many times can each branch be bent repeatedly?
A:

LED trees can be DIY shapes no matter how many times you branch the branches. But it’s better not to bend you light tree too often as that can cause loose connection between branches and trunk. If you find any loose, you can use the electrical tape to fix it.
Q:
Is it dangerous to use LED trees?
A:
Each one of tree includes power adapter. And output voltage is 24V which is safe for human being.
Q:
What if one of LED bulbs doesn’t work, will it affect the whole LED tree?
A:

This is not something that we want any of our customers to experience. But if one of the LED bulbs doesn’t work, it won’t affect the whole LED tree. It is suggested to remove the broken one and seal wrap up with electrical tape while turning off the tree.
